com.octo.android.robodemo
Class LabeledPoint

java.lang.Object
  android.graphics.Point
      com.octo.android.robodemo.LabeledPoint
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.os.Parcelable
public class LabeledPoint
extends android.graphics.Point
implements android.os.Parcelable

A pojo class that wraps all information needed to display a point on screen. LabeledPoint embed a position and a text to draw. The Drawable that illustrates this point will be provided by DrawView.getDrawViewAdapter(). This class implements Parcelable so that it can be passed between the Activity to illustrate and the DemoActivity.

Author:
sni
